getTextContents

public static java.lang.String getTextContents(org.w3c.dom.Node node)
Returns the contents of all immediate child text nodes, can strip whitespace

Takes a node as input and merges all its immediate text nodes into a string. If the strip whitespace flag is set, whitespace at the beggining and end of each merged text node will be removed

Parameters:
node - node to extract text contents of
Returns:
string containing text contents of the node
